      "instruction": "<p>While the veg is softening, top, tail and cut the <strong>courgettes </strong>in half through the middle, then slice the<strong> halved courgettes</strong>, lengthways into thin slices</p><p>Add the<strong> courgette slices </strong>to a tray (or two!) with 1/2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give it a good mix up</p><p>Add the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> to the oven and cook for 20-25 min or until softened and starting to colour</p>",
