    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 400ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[750ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>dried basil</strong> and <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>green lentils </strong>under<strong> cold running water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
