    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the veg has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and cook for a further 1 min</p><p>Add the<strong> rinsed lentils</strong> and<strong> tomato stock</strong> to the pan with the cooked veg</p><p>Cook, covered, for 20-25 min or until the lentils are almost tender – this is your <strong>lentil ragù</strong></p>",
