    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spoon<strong> half</strong> of the <strong>lentil ragù</strong> into an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, then top with a layer of <strong>roasted courgette slices</strong></p><p>Repeat this with the <strong>remaining lentil ragù</strong> and <strong>remaining roasted courgette slices</strong></p><p>Pour the <strong>béchamel sauce </strong>all over and top with the<strong> remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until bubbling and golden – this is your <strong>lighter</strong> <strong>lentil & courgette lasagne</strong></p>",
