    {
      "instruction": "<p>Leave the <strong>lighter</strong> <strong>lentil & courgette lasagne</strong> to stand for a few min before serving (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p><p>Wash the<strong> baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper<strong> </strong>and drizzle with a little<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> lighter</strong> <strong>lentil & courgette lasagne </strong>with the <strong>baby leaf</strong> <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
